---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Stay for Families — Preserve Generational Wisdom">
  <Header />

  <main class="pt-24">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="container-narrow text-center">
        <p class="text-ember text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4">For Families</p>
        <h1 class="heading-lg mb-6">
          Your family's stories<br/>
          <span class="text-ember">deserve to live forever.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="body-lg text-parchment-muted max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Grandparents' wisdom. Parents' love. Family recipes and traditions. Capture the voices that make your family unique — before they become memories themselves.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pain Point -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-void-50">
      <div class="container-narrow">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="heading-md mb-4">The voice you'll miss most</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-void p-8 border border-void-200">
            <p class="font-serif text-xl text-parchment mb-4 italic">
              "I have hundreds of photos of my grandmother, but I can barely remember her voice. What I wouldn't give for just one recording of her telling me a story."
            </p>
            <p class="text-parchment-muted text-sm">— Common regret</p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <p class="body-lg">
              We take thousands of photos but rarely capture voices. Yet it's the sound of a loved one speaking — their laugh, their cadence, their words of wisdom — that we miss most when they're gone.
            </p>
            <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted">
              Stey helps you capture what photos can't: the actual voice, stories, and personality of the people who matter most.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Use Cases -->
    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="container-wide">
        <h2 class="heading-md text-center mb-12">How families use Stey</h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-void-50 p-6 border border-void-200">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-ember/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif mb-3">Grandparent Interviews</h3>
            <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted">
              Use guided prompts to help grandparents share stories about their childhood, career, life lessons, and family history.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-void-50 p-6 border border-void-200">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-ember/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif mb-3">Letters to Children</h3>
            <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted">
              Parents recording messages, advice, and love for children to hear on future birthdays, graduations, or whenever they need it.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-void-50 p-6 border border-void-200">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-ember/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif mb-3">Family Recipes</h3>
            <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted">
              Grandma's secret recipes, explained in her own voice with all the tips and stories that make them special.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-void-50 p-6 border border-void-200">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-ember/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif mb-3">Immigration Stories</h3>
            <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted">
              First-generation stories of coming to a new country, preserved for descendants who need to know where they came from.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-void-50 p-6 border border-void-200">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-ember/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif mb-3">Holiday Traditions</h3>
            <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted">
              The why behind family traditions, explained by those who started them. So future generations understand the meaning.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-void-50 p-6 border border-void-200">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-ember/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif mb-3">Family Tree Context</h3>
            <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted">
              Stories about relatives — who they were, what they did, how they met. The context that brings a family tree to life.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Sample Prompts -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-void-50">
      <div class="container-narrow">
        <h2 class="heading-md text-center mb-8">Prompts to get started</h2>
        <p class="body-lg text-center text-parchment-muted mb-12">
          Not sure what to record? Here are some prompts perfect for family memories.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-void p-6 border border-void-200">
            <p class="font-serif text-lg text-ember">"What was your childhood home like? Tell me about your bedroom."</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-void p-6 border border-void-200">
            <p class="font-serif text-lg text-ember">"How did you meet Grandpa/Grandma? What was your first date?"</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-void p-6 border border-void-200">
            <p class="font-serif text-lg text-ember">"What's a lesson you learned the hard way that you want me to know?"</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-void p-6 border border-void-200">
            <p class="font-serif text-lg text-ember">"What were your parents like? What do you remember most about them?"</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-void p-6 border border-void-200">
            <p class="font-serif text-lg text-ember">"What's your happiest memory from when I was little?"</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-center text-parchment-muted mt-8">
          Stey includes 100+ guided prompts like these, organized by topic.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="container-narrow text-center">
        <h2 class="heading-md mb-6">Start preserving your family's stories today.</h2>
        <p class="body-lg text-parchment-muted mb-8">
          Every day that passes is a story that could be lost. Don't wait.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-parchment text-void px-8 py-4 font-medium hover:bg-ember transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M18.71 19.5c-.83 1.24-1.71 2.45-3.05 2.47-1.34.03-1.77-.79-3.29-.79-1.53 0-2 .77-3.27.82-1.31.05-2.3-1.32-3.14-2.53C4.25 17 2.94 12.45 4.7 9.39c.87-1.52 2.43-2.48 4.12-2.51 1.28-.02 2.5.87 3.29.87.78 0 2.26-1.07 3.81-.91.65.03 2.47.26 3.64 1.98-.09.06-2.17 1.28-2.15 3.81.03 3.02 2.65 4.03 2.68 4.04-.03.07-.42 1.44-1.38 2.83M13 3.5c.73-.83 1.94-1.46 2.94-1.5.13 1.17-.34 2.35-1.04 3.19-.69.85-1.83 1.51-2.95 1.42-.15-1.15.41-2.35 1.05-3.11z"/>
          </svg>
          Download for iOS — Free
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
